Ninja Combos
Ninja combat techniques build momentum in the wraps. When you use
combat abilities, the wraps remember recent techniques for a short
time. If three recent pieces line up, the wraps release a combo during
combat.

Resolving any three-piece combo also awards 10 Ninja GXP, in addition to
the GXP earned by its component skill attempts.

Some combinations have special results. Tsuki with Blind and Pummel
focuses armor-piercing force. Tsubo with Pummel strikes pressure points.
Pummel with Dimmak helps clear intoxication. Shuriken in a combo can
call a storm of throwing stars. Tsuki in a combo can add an extra strike.
Other combinations still release as a general burst of attacks.

Use <nskills> to review your abilities and watch the ninja line
in your monitor for recent combo pieces. Combo pieces fade quickly, so
combos reward active combat timing rather than long preparation.
